data.description: Presenting an extraordinary investment opportunity in the desirable Paradise Hills community! Introducing a captivating gem nestled within the coveted Ciobla High School district -- a meticulously designed 3-bedroom, 2-bath single-family haven built by Stillbrooks Homes. Home currently has a tenant until 6/30/2024 and will not move out until that date with rent at $1,725 per month. This elegant abode, encompassing a single inviting story, exudes both modern comfort and timeless charm. Upon entering, you're greeted by an open-concept living space, where natural light dances across gleaming hardwood floors. The spacious kitchen, adorned with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances, beckons to an aspiring chef. This home is available for showing by appointment.
